https://gruntjs.com

require: nodejs

Grunt command line interface: npm install -g grunt-cli

make a project folder

create package.json: npm init

install Grunt locally for your project: npm install grunt --save-dev

install plugins (https://gruntjs.com/plugins):
  npm install grunt-contrib-uglify --save-dev
  npm install grunt-contrib-sass --save-dev
  npm install grunt-contrib-cssmin --save-dev

Note:
  "grunt-contrib-sass" requires "npm install -g sass"

